products.title: Panama Oyster Roman Blind
products.description: Complete your interior with their panama oyster blind. With its cotton plain weave and timeless cream tones, this popular roman blind will frame your interior with style. The blind can be used in both traditional and contemporary interiors and adds a touch of simplicity to home renovation projects. Their panama range is available in a full range of colours so we are sure you will find the shade to compliment your interior.
